==Rivalries==
{{Main|South London derby}}
Charlton fans consider [[Millwall F.C.|Millwall]], [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]] and [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham]] as their rivals. Millwall's ground [[The Den]] and [[The Valley (London)|The Valley]] are just 4 miles apart.

