      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About||the possum species|Cuscus|the ancient Chilean village|Cuz Cuz}}

[[File:Couscous of Fes.JPG|thumb|256px|right|Couscous with vegetables and chickpeas]]
{{Infobox nutrition facts
  | serv_size_us = 1 cup
